			<common:synonyms xml:lang="en">PAM; Poly(2-propenamide); Polyacrylamide (PAA)</common:synonyms>
			<common:synonyms xml:lang="zh">PAM; Poly(2-propenamide); Polyacrylamide (PAA)</common:synonyms>
			<classificationInformation>
				<common:classification name="ILCD 1.1" classes="../ILCDClassification.xml">
					<common:class level="0">End-of-life treatment</common:class>
					<common:class level="1">Waste water treatment</common:class>
				</common:classification>
			</classificationInformation>
			<CASNumber>9003-05-8</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Polyacrylamide is an acrylic resin that is soluble in water. It is used in the treatment of industrial and municipal wastewater. Polyacrylamides are produced by the polymerization of acrylamide, a compound obtained by the hydration of acrylonitrile. It is a non-ionic, water-soluble, and biocompatible polymer that can be tailored to meet a broad range of applications. It finds applications in pulp and paper production, agriculture, food processing, mining, and as a flocculant in wastewater treatment.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">聚丙烯酰胺是一种可溶于水的丙烯酸树脂。它可用于处理工业和市政废水。聚丙烯酰胺由丙烯酰胺聚合而成，丙烯酰胺是一种由丙烯腈水合而成的化合物。它是一种非离子型、水溶性和生物相容性聚合物，可进行定制以满足广泛的应用需求。它可用于纸浆和纸张生产、农业、食品加工、采矿以及废水处理中的絮凝剂。</common:generalComment>
			<sumFormula>C3H5NO</sumFormula>
